name: GlobalGive
additional_notices: Kindly be aware that liquidity provided in Automated Market Maker platforms (eg. Uniswap, Sushiswap, Balancer) can be removed (also known as rug pulling), resulting in a collapse of available liquidity. Please exercise caution when trading! This notice is NOT directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder for our users.

description.en:
GlobalGive is a worldwide charity token with revolutionary tokenomics. GlobalGive uses the power of community engagement to perform monthly charitable donations based on a transaction fee redistribution model. 

We have a toxic whale tax built into our ecosystem to discourage large whale wallets from causing price dips, keeping the price stable and healthy. Anti bot measures have also been added to the contract code. 

We are a dedicated, fully doxxed and public team from multiple countries. We are here to change the world, one donation at a time.
